own 17 live "public-readme-english-only — no CJK in public READMEs"
  slug public-readme-english-only
  decl ~/core/hexa-lang/tool/readme_english_audit.hexa .own
  scope need-singularity org 5 repos (n6-architecture, nexus, hexa-lang, anima, papers) root README.md — no Hangul (AC00..D7AF / Jamo) / Kana (Hiragana / Katakana) / CJK Unified (4E00..9FFF). Greek (sigma phi tau), Math (subscripts, arrows, relations), common punctuation (checkmark, em dash, ellipsis), and SI units pass.
  status live
  since 2026-04-21
  why Enforcement path for own#1 doc-english-required. Manual review missed 158+ long-tail fragments. arXiv compatibility + international contribution + org landing consistency. Scope promoted to raw#33 ai-native-english-only (2026-04-21).
  verify hexa ~/core/hexa-lang/tool/readme_english_audit.hexa
  cron on-commit
  on_fail block
  label public README English-only gate
  deps own:doc-english-required own:readme-sealed-required raw:ai-native-english-only

